			<div class="content" id="post-content-1766654">
									

<p>Hi, I'm the creator of the SCP-610 game. I thought it was time to bring this game up to the site that inspired it. I'm not sure how many of you here know &quot;or care&quot; about this game, but I figure I should post a topic about it.</p>
<p><strong>Game Mechanics</strong></p>
<p>-You have gas mask that you have to keep on around the infected,but it blocks some of your vision.</p>
<p>- While you do have an assault rifle and sidearm your low on ammo and guns do not do to much to the infected in less you fill them with bullets.</p>
<p>-Infected are very deadly even when there is only one.</p>
<p>-While you are a trained Foundation member you can not last forever. You need to get out without becoming infected.</p>
<p>-Any of your Surviving squad members can and will die or become infected.</p>
<p>-Hand to Hand combat is very dangerous with infected, as your risk of becoming infected are much higher.</p>
<p>-You will have to deal with crazed and desperate suvivors.</p>
