<p><strong>Story Prologue</strong><br />
You are a guard stationed at a Foundation Site near the containment zone of SCP-610. Your day is going on as normal, for the Foundation, of course. While you're collecting yourself in your room; the site's sirens start,gunfire and screaming begins to blare out from your radio. As you try to figure out what's happening your hear <em>&quot;SCP-610 has escaped it's containment zone and is rapidly overrunning the site! Full site quarantine is priority! On-Site warheads are to be activated ASA-*Distorted Screams* *Gun Fire*</em>. After that you find yourself standing in silence. Alone. Little to no chance of survival.</p>
<p>I would like to hear your thoughts and comments about the game. Also be tell me about <em>any</em> issues you have or things think I'm doing wrong. But try to keep it constructive</p>
<p>Thank you<br />
Kind Regards<br />
-BJFowLer</p>
